author: Al Jazeera
title: 'Strike again': US scientist predicts coronavirus return in fall
description: But Dr Anthony Fauci says if the virus does re-emerge, it would not be a repeat of the major crisis the US faces now.
content:
Coronavirus will likely "strike again" in the fall in the United States, according to the top American scientist tackling the disease.
